This is a small version of [gg_marbletemple_v2](http://www.gamebanana.com/maps/110182 "gg_marbletemple_v2") i made a long time ago.  Imo the map was way to big so i decided to create a smaller version...and here is the result. 

it is better than the big version, because:

+it contains a lot of cubemaps
+some props and debris brushes
+2 mini fountains (just water bowls)
+way better lightning...now you will see everything and everyone. 

Enjoy! 32 Players maximum

Made by tom_tom. Gungame based on a dust style look with a new twist while in the desert. Both sides are equally matched with a unground path, and main building. added dust and wind to contribute to the looks. placed player clips to stop catching to the door/window frames to ensure no 'stupid' accidental deaths because of getting stuck. Made sure there no way to get caught on top of door/window frames as well. placed blocks and made sure all drops don't cause damage besides jumping off the roof of corse. maximum players is 24.
